attributes.body: Pharmers Quality Concentrates is New Mexico’s premier manufacture of high-end concentrates. We are the chemistry focused cannabis extraction laboratory in Socorro, New Mexico. We strive to provide the highest quality cannabis oil available by imploring the use of modern organic chemistry. We specialize in cannabinoid extraction, distillation, isolation, and remediation of contaminants. We believe it is important to trust the source of your medicine. Along time ago before marijuana prohibition, people were able to purchase Cannabis Oil at Pharmacies across the country. These pharmacies sold classily, trusted brands of medicine made by chemists with a true want to help and provide relief to their consumers. These brands were proud and stood by their medicine and so do we. Our motto is QUALITY COMES STANDARD because we believe it should! Our highly qualified staff of Laboratory Technicians will ensure that the utmost care is taken in the handling, extraction, and processing of your Cannabis oils. Selection of quality biomass is key to obtaining the best tasting and greater yielding concentrates. Let us work with your company to provide your patients with the best medication in New Mexico.

attributes.name: Pumpkin Pie | Distillate Cart
attributes.body: CONTROLLED EXTRACTIONREMEDIATIONDISTILLATION We achieve Molecular Perfection within our Premium Distillate products via methodologies found commonly in other industries. Much like filtered water, cooking oils and other natural plant oil products, refinement is used to isolate specific desired compounds found with the different organic starting materials. Cannabis is a complex organic plant material that contains compounds which are not considered “healthy” for ingestion or inhalation via vaporization. The predominant compounds within cannabis that interest us are called “Cannabinoids”. A plethora of data and litereture suggest that cannabinoids are beneficial to many aspects of human health. Through refinement and isolation we can offer consumers a clean way to enjoy cannabinoids without plant volatiles, waxes and fats found in pre-processed cannabis biomass materials or crude extracts. At Pharmers, we employ methods of modern chemistry to refine crude cannabis extract into a pure, cannabinoid rich, odorless, and tasteless distillate oil. Demonstrated through decades of experience in extracting and refining, our founder Don Romero, properly named “The Distillate Don”, became a trusted source of education and consultation for industry giants from coast to coast. With Don at the helm, Pharmers Quality has established itself nationally as the expert level extraction and distillation specialists. What makes our oil different? It’s simple, purity through proper processes. When enjoying Pharmers, the consumer can trust they have a safe, clean, and pure product in their hands.

attributes.name: HIBEGONE
attributes.body: HIBEGONE is a versatile 2 in 1 product that can aid in mitigating the effects of cannabis if you become overly intoxicated OR assist in lowering your tolerance level for a more optimal high. Recover: Consume HIBEGONE if you become TOO high. Expect to feel the effects diminish within 15-30 minutes. Reduce: Take HIBEGONE when sober upon waking up. Allow at least 8 hours for HIBEGONE's process to fully take effect. Experience the enjoyment of cannabis as if it were your first time again. *Results may vary from person to person. HIBEGONE may cause you to fail a drug test*

Prohibition 37 flower is our specialty and what we have built our brand on. Our production facilities include 2 state-of-the-art indoor cultivations totaling 14,000 sq ft in our home city of Albuquerque. We also have an outdoor farm in Belen, and greenhouse productions in Belen and Gallup. Our mission is to destigmatize the industry, produce outstanding quality cannabis, and positively contribute to the quality of life of our patients and customers. We currently grow over 75 cultivars, and are continually adding the newest and most sought after genetics to bring to every corner of New Mexico. WHO IS P37? Prohibition 37 is a physician-led, nationally recognized, and award-winning vertical cannabis company. P37 is highly focused on the customer experience and science of the medicinal and recreational effects of its many products. Our name is derived from The Marihuana Tax Act of 1937, which was a U.S. federal law that effectively criminalized the possession and distribution of marijuana. While it did not directly ban the cannabis plant, it imposed strict regulations and heavy taxes on its cultivation, sales, and use. This made it impossible to legally engage in these activities, leading to a de facto prohibition of cannabis. The Act played a significant role in shaping the modern approach to marijuana regulation in the United States.\ SOCIAL EQUITY AND JUSTICE The Marihuana Tax Act of 1937 disproportionately targeted minorities, particularly African, Mexican, and Jewish American communities. While the act did not explicitly mention racial or ethnic groups, its implementation and enforcement were marked by tremendous racial bias and discrimination. Law enforcement, for example, selectively targeted and arrested individuals from minority groups and used marijuana-related offenses as a pretext for discriminatory actions. This contributed to the disproportionate impact of the Act on minorities, perpetuating racial stereotypes and injustices for generations to come. Our mission at Prohibition 37 is to reverse decades of cannabis-related injustice and create a healthy, communal, and scientific approach to cannabis use.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Concord Cream
attributes.body: Concord Cream, a predominantly Indica strain, is the sweet sweet love child of Grape Bubba and Cookies & Cream. This soothing bud, rich in flavor, is a must-try for any grape strain fans. True to its name, Concord Cream boasts a super sweet and creamy fruity grape flavor complemented by notes of flowery violet and vanilla. The aroma mirrors this profile with a hint of sour grapefruit. Concord Cream is a favored choice for addressing various conditions across a whole spectrum, including stress, anxiety, muscle spasms, cramps, depression, and insomnia. The Concord Cream high unfolds gradually, initiating with a slow burn of euphoria that melts the mad/sad away. Concord Cream is wonderful for consumers that have social anxiety as its a very talkative, giggly strain! As the mental boost persists, a sense of physical relaxation takes over, eventually inducing a sleepy, sedative state.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Lemon Skunk
attributes.body: Lemon Skunk is a Sativa Strain with a citrusy/skunky "Punch You In The Face" aroma and balanced effects. Lemon Skunk has dense, trichome-covered buds with vibrant green and orange hues with a higher than average THC content. Lemon Skunk is effective for people with Depression, Stress, and Nausea, with none of the energy that comes from your usual sativa.

attributes.name: Grape Dane | Disposable
attributes.body: Live Extraction As opposed to drying and curing, the essence of the living cannabis plant is preserved through freezing immediately after harvest and remaining frozen throughout extraction. This process retains a broader spectrum of live terpenes and cannabinoids in higher volumes, yielding an exotic alternative to traditional BHO extracts. Live BHO typically resembles that of the plant in its final stage of flowering when terpene potency is at its peak generating robust aromatics and delivering unmatched piquancy. Adding enticing nuances to the typical cannabis extract palate, live extracts have become the first choice of the modern connoisseur. Traditional Extraction Utilizing dried and cured cannabis, this process extracts the cannabinoids, along with the aroma and flavor of the plant you love into a powerful concentrate. The best extracts of cannabis leave behind many of the carcinogenic substances the plants produce while preserving the desirable contents they contain. Cannabis extract can manifest a variety of dynamic textures, consistencies, and useful by-products such as H.T.S.F.E. Furthermore, cannabis extract has become the industry’s preferred method for infusing activated cannabinoids, such as ?9-THC, into ingestible and topical products. Refined Extraction Take into consideration the environmental pollutants and agricultural contaminants that can be associated with cannabis cultivation, the subsequent extracts can contain unwanted impurities, pigments, and even harmful chemicals. Our proprietary filtration techniques and chromatography methodologies allow us to remediate compromised or otherwise undesirable extracts while maintaining the desirable components such as cannabinoids and terpenes. The end result meets all standards for consumption from shelf-ready solid extract to liquid and food-grade variations. By making these processes available, we aim to help eliminate large-scale waste associated with the ever-expanding industry of commercial cannabis.

attributes.name: AiroPod - GSC - Hybrid - .5g
attributes.body:
AiroPod Strain Series .5g Cartridge

• Strain Series

• Hybrid

• GSC

• Pure Distillate Oil

• Full Terpene Profile

• High Potency

 

The AiroPod cartridge is more than a stylish magnet, it’s the first vessel of its kind. The secured mouthpiece and filling septum minimize the possibility of leakage, something which has been a common issue among older model vaporizers. Considering that risk of accidental exposure, to children or pets for example, the AiroPod cartridge was built for safety as well as durability.

Free from a traditional wick and coil setup, AiroPod cartridges adopted ceramic reactor technology to serve as the heating element. Unmatched thermal precision ensures concentrates are always vaporized at the proper temperature. This preserves the flavor of concentrates and prevents them from burning. The silver-plated magnetic base makes exchanging cartridges a snap, while ensuring a solid connection every time.
